snippet.title: Drag Racing Trailer (Google)
snippet.description:
Drag Racing is the classic nitro fuelled racing game for Android! 

Get it on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.creativemobile.DragRacing 

Race, Tune, Upgrade and Customize 50+ real licensed cars from the world’s hottest car manufacturers.

Climb the leaderboards and immortalize your name in the Hall of Fame! Challenge other players online: race 1 on 1, drive your opponent’s car, or participate in real-time 10-player races in Pro League
